Release notes
Sourced from conan's releases.

1.25.2 (19-May-2020)

Bugfix: Previously conan always set cpp_std option in meson project, even if cppstd option was not set in conan profile. Now it sets the option only if cppstd profile option has a concrete value. (conan-io/conan#7047)
Bugfix: Fix deploy generator management of relative symlinks. (conan-io/conan#7044)
Bugfix: Fixes an issue where Apple Framework lookup wasn't working on RelWithDebInfo. (conan-io/conan#7041)
Bugfix: Fix broken AutoToolsBuildEnvironment when a profile:build is defined. (conan-io/conan#7032)




